                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18371127-214-offence-1 t18371127-cd-168"></join>27th of October</rs>, 2 heifers, price 19<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., the property of <persName id="t18371127-name-1198" type="victimName">
